snippet.title: Kine Date Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
KINE is a 3D narrative puzzle game about three quirky machines that aspire to be musicians. Embark across a theatrical dreamscape by solving a wide variety of challenging 3D puzzles. Guide Euler, Quat, and Roo as they struggle to form a band and find their big break!

https://www.epicgames.com/store/en-US/product/kine/home
